</style><script type="text/javascript">function cxIsArticlePage() {
  return cxdj.getUtagData().page_content_type && cxdj.getUtagData().page_content_type === 'Article';
}

function callExternalModule(widgetId, targetElementId){
  cX.CCE.run({
    'widgetId' : widgetId,
    'targetElementId' : targetElementId,
  });
}

function cxCallSeparateModules(){
  //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience FALLBACK...');

  var topRhsPlaceholder = document.querySelector('#cx-popup');
  var candybarPlaceholder = document.querySelector('#cx-candybar');
  var marketingTilePlaceholder = document.querySelector('#cx-membsership-tile');

  // HP and Section Fronts
  if(window.location.pathname === '/' || !cxIsArticlePage()){
	//console.log('[cx] Unified Experience : HP Handling ...');

    //Top RHS is always present , else this module itself wouldn't be invoked.
    //console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback for Homepage: Top RHS...');
    callExternalModule('2de24eadb5f96a9436a375f0d2087dac83093d90', 'cx-popup');

    if(candybarPlaceholder){ // Candybar may not be present on all HPs/SFs
      //console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback: Candybar');
      switch (cxdj.meta.edition) {
        case 'naus':
          callExternalModule('15fc5810f60a3ecdf05c10bbdab82744dbc95213', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiajp':
          callExternalModule('46c976a6d4479e4ec8c96b13fb9e002f6eb68265', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiacn':
          callExternalModule('1c7cfe13eb4ae0e594dba0323f1864e905fb5e0a', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiacn_hant':
          callExternalModule('45f5ca6fa134b605506a7668f140843ef8751248', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
      }
      
    }
    if(marketingTilePlaceholder){  // MT  may not be present on all HPs/SFs
      //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience Fallback MT found - calling MT' );  
      callExternalModule('9e5724d5eda30e7c52430d3a5113fed1ed60d22a', 'cx-membership-tile');
    }
  } else if(cxIsArticlePage && cxdj.meta.pwType === 'free'){
    //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience : Free Article...');

    //Top RHS is always present , else this module itself wouldn't be invoked.
	//console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback for FREE Article: Top RHS...');
    callExternalModule('2de24eadb5f96a9436a375f0d2087dac83093d90', 'cx-popup');

    if(candybarPlaceholder){ // Candybar may not be present on all Free Articles
      //console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback for FREE Article: Candybar');
      switch (cxdj.meta.edition) {
        case 'naus':
          callExternalModule('15fc5810f60a3ecdf05c10bbdab82744dbc95213', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiajp':
          callExternalModule('46c976a6d4479e4ec8c96b13fb9e002f6eb68265', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiacn':
          callExternalModule('1c7cfe13eb4ae0e594dba0323f1864e905fb5e0a', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiacn_hant':
          callExternalModule('45f5ca6fa134b605506a7668f140843ef8751248', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
      }
    }
  } else if(cxIsArticlePage && cxdj.meta.pwType != 'free'){
    //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience : LOCKED  Article...');
    //Top RHS is always present , else this module itself wouldn't be invoked.
    //console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback for LOCKED Article: Top RHS only');
    callExternalModule('2de24eadb5f96a9436a375f0d2087dac83093d90', 'cx-popup');
  } else{
    //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience : unk');
  }
}

function cxHandleTemplateDeliverySeparation(){ 
  //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience Creative');

  window.requestAnimationFrame(function(){

    handlePopoutMouseOver();
    handlePopoutMouseLeave();
    handleRepositionMessageElements();
    handleCBClose();

    function handleCBClose(){
      var $cb = document.querySelector('#cx-candybar') || document.querySelector('#cx-candybar-wrap');
      if($cb){
        var $closeIcon = $cb.querySelector('.close-btn');
        if (!$closeIcon) { return; }
        $closeIcon.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
          $cb.classList.add('fade-out');
          $cb.remove();
        });
      }
    }

    function handleRepositionMessageElements(){

      var popoutMessage = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs'); 
      var popoutMessageTargetEl = document.querySelector('#cx-popup');
      var memberTileMessage = document.querySelector('#cx-member-tile-wrapper');
      var memberTileMessageTargetEl = document.querySelector('#cx-membership-tile');
      var candybarMessage = document.querySelector('#cx-candybar-wrap');
      var candybarMessageTargetEl = document.querySelector('#cx-candybar');

      if(popoutMessage && popoutMessageTargetEl){
        popoutMessageTargetEl.appendChild(popoutMessage);
        popoutMessage.style.display = 'block';
      }
      if(memberTileMessage && memberTileMessageTargetEl){
        memberTileMessageTargetEl.appendChild(memberTileMessage);
        memberTileMessage.style.display = 'flex';
      }
      if(candybarMessage && candybarMessageTargetEl){
        candybarMessageTargetEl.appendChild(candybarMessage);
        candybarMessage.style.display = 'block';
      }

    }

    function handlePopoutMouseOver() {
      var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs');
      var $popout = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs .popout');
      if (!$popout) { return; }

      $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseover', function (event) {
        event.stopPropagation();
        $popout.classList.remove('hide');
        $popout.classList.add('show');
        $popout.classList.remove('fade-out');
        $popout.classList.add('fade-in');
      });
    }

    function handlePopoutMouseLeave() {
      var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs'); 
      var $popout = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs .popout'); 
      if (!$popout) { return; }

      $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseleave', function (event) {
        event.stopPropagation();
        $popout.classList.remove('fade-in');
        $popout.classList.add('fade-out');

        setTimeout(function () {
          $popout.classList.remove('show');
          $popout.classList.add('hide');
        }, 250);
      });
    }

  });

}</script><style type="text/css">#cx-notification-wrapper .notification-msg {

</style><script type="text/javascript">window.requestAnimationFrame(function() {
  handleCloseButtonClick();

  function handleCloseButtonClick() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $closeButton = $wrapper.querySelector('.close-btn');
    if (!$closeButton) { return; }


    var campaignData;
    try {
      campaignData = JSON.parse($wrapper.dataset.campaign);
    } catch(e) {
      campaignData = {};
    }

    $closeButton.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      campaignData.hideType = 'closeButton';

      if ($closeButton.className.indexOf('gdpr-close') > -1) {
        cxdj.trackPolicy('wsjcpoct2017');
      } else {
        if (campaignData.suppressId) {
          cxdj.annotateUserProfile(campaignData.suppressId);
        }
        cxdj.reportInteractionEvent('notificationClose', campaignData);
      }
      cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50);
    });
  }
});

function cxHandlePageNotificationOmniChannelCheck(item) {
  var campaignData = cxenseOffers.getCampaignData(item);
  cxdj.reportInteractionEvent('notificationView', campaignData);
}

function cxHandlePageNotificationCtaButtonClick(item) {
  var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper');
  var campaignData = cxenseOffers.getCampaignData(item);
  var currentUrl;

  if (window.location.href) {
    currentUrl = encodeURIComponent(window.location.href.replace(window.location.search, ''));
  }

  cxGetRenewUrl(item, function () {
    //Auto Suppress on Button Click if a Suppress Value is found
    if (campaignData.suppressId) {
      cxdj.annotateUserProfile(campaignData.suppressId);
    }
    var redirectUrl = addCurrentUrlToEduRedirectUrl(currentUrl, item.url);

    if (item.campaign === '195' || item.campaign === '130') {
      addTokentoRedirectUrl(redirectUrl, function (redirectUrl) {
        cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50, function () {
          window.location.href = redirectUrl;
        });
      });
    } else {
      cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50, function () {
        window.location.href = redirectUrl;
      });
    }
  });

  function addTokentoRedirectUrl(url, cb) {
    if (!url || url.length === 0) { return; }

    var key = 'wsj-mansion-global-token';

    cxenseOffers.get1stPartyData(key, function (error, token) {
      url += (url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?') + 'token=' + token;
      if (typeof cb === 'function') {
        cb(url);
      }
    });
  }

  function addCurrentUrlToEduRedirectUrl(currentUrl, url) {
    var reg = /^(http|https)?:\/\/(partner\.wsj\.com\/partner\/)([^\/]|[^\?])*$/i;
    var insertPosition;

    if (reg.test(url)) {
      insertPosition = url.indexOf('?');

      if (insertPosition > 0) {
        url = url.substring(0, insertPosition) + (url[insertPosition - 1] === '/' ? '' : '/') + currentUrl + url.substring(insertPosition);
      } else {
        url += (url[url.length - 1] === '/' ? '' : '/') + currentUrl;
      }
    }
    return url;
  }
}

function hok3RaV1() {
  document.querySelector('body').classList.add('hok-3R-V1');

  window.requestAnimationFrame(function () {
    //change description copy
    var copy = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper .notification-description');
    copy.innerText = 'The credit card we have on file for your WSJ membership may be invalid. To avoid any unintended interruptions to your service, please take a moment to update your credit card details now.';

    //change CTA copy
    var cta = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper .notification-action a');
    cta.innerText = 'UPDATE MY CREDIT CARD';

    //change CTA url
    cta.href = 'https://customercenter.wsj.com/payment';

    //pushing the navigation bar down if the banner is visible
    var topDiv = document.querySelector('.style__hat_1vqyrZZ3j7vMCXYKbvaqKa');
    var bannerVisibleOrNot = setInterval(function () {
      if (document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper').style.display !== 'none') {
        clearInterval(bannerVisibleOrNot);
        topDiv.style.marginBottom = '57px';
      } else if (document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper').style.display === 'none') {
        clearInterval(bannerVisibleOrNot);
        topDiv.style.marginBottom = '0px';
      }
    }, 50);

  });

}

function cxHandlePageNotificationAdobeIdCtaButtonClick(item) {
  var redirectUrl = addAdobeIdToRedirectUrl(item.url);
  window.location.href = redirectUrl;

  function addAdobeIdToRedirectUrl(url) {
    if (!url || url.length === 0) { return; }

    var adobeCookie = cxdj.getOmnitureCookieValue();
    if (adobeCookie && adobeCookie.mcmid) {
      url += (url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?') + 'adobeid=' + adobeCookie.mcmid;
    }
    return url;
  }
}

function cxHandlePageNotificationVxidCtaButtonClick(item) {
  var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper');
  var campaignData = cxenseOffers.getCampaignData(item);

  cxGetRenewUrl(item, function () {
    //Auto Suppress on Button Click if a Suppress Value is found
    if (campaignData.suppressId) {
      cxdj.annotateUserProfile(campaignData.suppressId);
    }

    var redirectUrl = addVxidToRedirectUrl(item.url);
    cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50, function () {
      window.location.href = redirectUrl;
    });
  });

  function addVxidToRedirectUrl(url) {
    if (!url || url.length === 0) { return; }

    var vxid = cxenseOffers.getVxid();
    url += (url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?') + 'vxid=' + vxid;

    return url;
  }
}

function cxGetRenewUrl(item, cb) {
  var trackCode = item['Track Code'] || 'default';

  if (item['Message Id'] === "on_renew") {
    cxenseOffers.getUserRenewLink(trackCode, function (error, url) {
      if (!error && url) {
        item.url = url;
      }
      if (typeof cb === 'function') {
        cb();
      }
    });
  } else {
    if (typeof cb === 'function') {
      cb();
    }
  }
}

//EDU Redirect May 2022
function cxHandle1PDRedirect(){

  function cb(partialUrl){
    //redirect valid URLs
    var reg = /^(http|https)?:\/\/(partner\.wsj\.com\/p\/)([^\/]|[^\?])*$/i;
    if (reg.test(partialUrl)) {
      window.location.href = partialUrl;
    } else {
      var url = "https://partner.wsj.com/" + redirectUrlSuffix;
      window.location.href = url;
    }
  }

  var key = 'wsj-facultystaffrefresh-ctaurl';
  cxenseOffers.get1stPartyData(key, function (error, partialUrl) {
    if (typeof cb === 'function') {
      cb(partialUrl);
    } 
  });

function cxGetRenewUrl(item, cb) {
  var trackCode = item['Track Code'] || 'default';

  if (item['Message Id'] === "on_renew") {
    cxenseOffers.getUserRenewLink(trackCode, function (error, url) {
      if (!error && url) {
        item.url = url;

        cb();
      }
    });

    if (typeof cb === 'function') {
      cb();
    }
  }
}

/*  === Candybar ===  */

#cx-candybar-wrap{
  position: fixed;
  left: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  width:100%;

</style><script type="text/javascript">function cxIsArticlePage() {
  return cxdj.getUtagData().page_content_type && cxdj.getUtagData().page_content_type === 'Article';
}

function callExternalModule(widgetId, targetElementId){
  cX.CCE.run({
    'widgetId' : widgetId,
    'targetElementId' : targetElementId,
  });
}

function cxCallSeparateModules(){
  //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience FALLBACK...');

  var topRhsPlaceholder = document.querySelector('#cx-popup');
  var candybarPlaceholder = document.querySelector('#cx-candybar');
  var marketingTilePlaceholder = document.querySelector('#cx-membsership-tile');

  // HP and Section Fronts
  if(window.location.pathname === '/' || !cxIsArticlePage()){
	//console.log('[cx] Unified Experience : HP Handling ...');

    //Top RHS is always present , else this module itself wouldn't be invoked.
    //console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback for Homepage: Top RHS...');
    callExternalModule('2de24eadb5f96a9436a375f0d2087dac83093d90', 'cx-popup');

    if(candybarPlaceholder){ // Candybar may not be present on all HPs/SFs
      //console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback: Candybar');
      switch (cxdj.meta.edition) {
        case 'naus':
          callExternalModule('15fc5810f60a3ecdf05c10bbdab82744dbc95213', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiajp':
          callExternalModule('46c976a6d4479e4ec8c96b13fb9e002f6eb68265', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiacn':
          callExternalModule('1c7cfe13eb4ae0e594dba0323f1864e905fb5e0a', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiacn_hant':
          callExternalModule('45f5ca6fa134b605506a7668f140843ef8751248', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
      }
      
    }
    if(marketingTilePlaceholder){  // MT  may not be present on all HPs/SFs
      //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience Fallback MT found - calling MT' );  
      callExternalModule('9e5724d5eda30e7c52430d3a5113fed1ed60d22a', 'cx-membership-tile');
    }
  } else if(cxIsArticlePage && cxdj.meta.pwType === 'free'){
    //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience : Free Article...');

    //Top RHS is always present , else this module itself wouldn't be invoked.
	//console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback for FREE Article: Top RHS...');
    callExternalModule('2de24eadb5f96a9436a375f0d2087dac83093d90', 'cx-popup');

    if(candybarPlaceholder){ // Candybar may not be present on all Free Articles
      //console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback for FREE Article: Candybar');
      switch (cxdj.meta.edition) {
        case 'naus':
          callExternalModule('15fc5810f60a3ecdf05c10bbdab82744dbc95213', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiajp':
          callExternalModule('46c976a6d4479e4ec8c96b13fb9e002f6eb68265', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiacn':
          callExternalModule('1c7cfe13eb4ae0e594dba0323f1864e905fb5e0a', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
        case 'asiacn_hant':
          callExternalModule('45f5ca6fa134b605506a7668f140843ef8751248', 'cx-candybar');
          break;
      }
    }
  } else if(cxIsArticlePage && cxdj.meta.pwType != 'free'){
    //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience : LOCKED  Article...');
    //Top RHS is always present , else this module itself wouldn't be invoked.
    //console.log('[cx] Calling Fallback for LOCKED Article: Top RHS only');
    callExternalModule('2de24eadb5f96a9436a375f0d2087dac83093d90', 'cx-popup');
  } else{
    //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience : unk');
  }
}

function cxHandleTemplateDeliverySeparation(){ 
  //console.log('[cx] Unified Experience Creative');

  window.requestAnimationFrame(function(){

    handlePopoutMouseOver();
    handlePopoutMouseLeave();
    handleRepositionMessageElements();
    handleCBClose();

    function handleCBClose(){
      var $cb = document.querySelector('#cx-candybar') || document.querySelector('#cx-candybar-wrap');
      if($cb){
        var $closeIcon = $cb.querySelector('.close-btn');
        if (!$closeIcon) { return; }
        $closeIcon.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
          $cb.classList.add('fade-out');
          $cb.remove();
        });
      }
    }

    function handleRepositionMessageElements(){

      var popoutMessage = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs'); 
      var popoutMessageTargetEl = document.querySelector('#cx-popup');
      var memberTileMessage = document.querySelector('#cx-member-tile-wrapper');
      var memberTileMessageTargetEl = document.querySelector('#cx-membership-tile');
      var candybarMessage = document.querySelector('#cx-candybar-wrap');
      var candybarMessageTargetEl = document.querySelector('#cx-candybar');

      if(popoutMessage && popoutMessageTargetEl){
        popoutMessageTargetEl.appendChild(popoutMessage);
        popoutMessage.style.display = 'block';
      }
      if(memberTileMessage && memberTileMessageTargetEl){
        memberTileMessageTargetEl.appendChild(memberTileMessage);
        memberTileMessage.style.display = 'flex';
      }
      if(candybarMessage && candybarMessageTargetEl){
        candybarMessageTargetEl.appendChild(candybarMessage);
        candybarMessage.style.display = 'block';
      }

    }

    function handlePopoutMouseOver() {
      var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs');
      var $popout = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs .popout');
      if (!$popout) { return; }

      $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseover', function (event) {
        event.stopPropagation();
        $popout.classList.remove('hide');
        $popout.classList.add('show');
        $popout.classList.remove('fade-out');
        $popout.classList.add('fade-in');
      });
    }

    function handlePopoutMouseLeave() {
      var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs'); 
      var $popout = document.querySelector('#cx-top-rhs .popout'); 
      if (!$popout) { return; }

      $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseleave', function (event) {
        event.stopPropagation();
        $popout.classList.remove('fade-in');
        $popout.classList.add('fade-out');

        setTimeout(function () {
          $popout.classList.remove('show');
          $popout.classList.add('hide');
        }, 250);
      });
    }

  });

</style><script type="text/javascript">window.requestAnimationFrame(function() {
  handleCloseButtonClick();

  function handleCloseButtonClick() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $closeButton = $wrapper.querySelector('.close-btn');
    if (!$closeButton) { return; }


    var campaignData;
    try {
      campaignData = JSON.parse($wrapper.dataset.campaign);
    } catch(e) {
      campaignData = {};
    }

    $closeButton.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      campaignData.hideType = 'closeButton';

      if ($closeButton.className.indexOf('gdpr-close') > -1) {
        cxdj.trackPolicy('wsjcpoct2017');
      } else {
        if (campaignData.suppressId) {
          cxdj.annotateUserProfile(campaignData.suppressId);
        }
        cxdj.reportInteractionEvent('notificationClose', campaignData);
      }
      cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50);
    });
  }
});

function cxHandlePageNotificationOmniChannelCheck(item) {
  var campaignData = cxenseOffers.getCampaignData(item);
  cxdj.reportInteractionEvent('notificationView', campaignData);
}

function cxHandlePageNotificationCtaButtonClick(item) {
  var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper');
  var campaignData = cxenseOffers.getCampaignData(item);
  var currentUrl;

  if (window.location.href) {
    currentUrl = encodeURIComponent(window.location.href.replace(window.location.search, ''));
  }

  cxGetRenewUrl(item, function () {
    //Auto Suppress on Button Click if a Suppress Value is found
    if (campaignData.suppressId) {
      cxdj.annotateUserProfile(campaignData.suppressId);
    }
    var redirectUrl = addCurrentUrlToEduRedirectUrl(currentUrl, item.url);

    if (item.campaign === '195' || item.campaign === '130') {
      addTokentoRedirectUrl(redirectUrl, function (redirectUrl) {
        cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50, function () {
          window.location.href = redirectUrl;
        });
      });
    } else {
      cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50, function () {
        window.location.href = redirectUrl;
      });
    }
  });

  function addTokentoRedirectUrl(url, cb) {
    if (!url || url.length === 0) { return; }

    var key = 'wsj-mansion-global-token';

    cxenseOffers.get1stPartyData(key, function (error, token) {
      url += (url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?') + 'token=' + token;
      if (typeof cb === 'function') {
        cb(url);
      }
    });
  }

  function addCurrentUrlToEduRedirectUrl(currentUrl, url) {
    var reg = /^(http|https)?:\/\/(partner\.wsj\.com\/partner\/)([^\/]|[^\?])*$/i;
    var insertPosition;

    if (reg.test(url)) {
      insertPosition = url.indexOf('?');

      if (insertPosition > 0) {
        url = url.substring(0, insertPosition) + (url[insertPosition - 1] === '/' ? '' : '/') + currentUrl + url.substring(insertPosition);
      } else {
        url += (url[url.length - 1] === '/' ? '' : '/') + currentUrl;
      }
    }
    return url;
  }
}

function hok3RaV1() {
  document.querySelector('body').classList.add('hok-3R-V1');

  window.requestAnimationFrame(function () {
    //change description copy
    var copy = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper .notification-description');
    copy.innerText = 'The credit card we have on file for your WSJ membership may be invalid. To avoid any unintended interruptions to your service, please take a moment to update your credit card details now.';

    //change CTA copy
    var cta = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper .notification-action a');
    cta.innerText = 'UPDATE MY CREDIT CARD';

    //change CTA url
    cta.href = 'https://customercenter.wsj.com/payment';

    //pushing the navigation bar down if the banner is visible
    var topDiv = document.querySelector('.style__hat_1vqyrZZ3j7vMCXYKbvaqKa');
    var bannerVisibleOrNot = setInterval(function () {
      if (document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper').style.display !== 'none') {
        clearInterval(bannerVisibleOrNot);
        topDiv.style.marginBottom = '57px';
      } else if (document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper').style.display === 'none') {
        clearInterval(bannerVisibleOrNot);
        topDiv.style.marginBottom = '0px';
      }
    }, 50);

  });

}

function cxHandlePageNotificationAdobeIdCtaButtonClick(item) {
  var redirectUrl = addAdobeIdToRedirectUrl(item.url);
  window.location.href = redirectUrl;

  function addAdobeIdToRedirectUrl(url) {
    if (!url || url.length === 0) { return; }

    var adobeCookie = cxdj.getOmnitureCookieValue();
    if (adobeCookie && adobeCookie.mcmid) {
      url += (url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?') + 'adobeid=' + adobeCookie.mcmid;
    }
    return url;
  }
}

function cxHandlePageNotificationVxidCtaButtonClick(item) {
  var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper');
  var campaignData = cxenseOffers.getCampaignData(item);

  cxGetRenewUrl(item, function () {
    //Auto Suppress on Button Click if a Suppress Value is found
    if (campaignData.suppressId) {
      cxdj.annotateUserProfile(campaignData.suppressId);
    }

    var redirectUrl = addVxidToRedirectUrl(item.url);
    cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50, function () {
      window.location.href = redirectUrl;
    });
  });

  function addVxidToRedirectUrl(url) {
    if (!url || url.length === 0) { return; }

    var vxid = cxenseOffers.getVxid();
    url += (url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?') + 'vxid=' + vxid;

    return url;
  }
}

function cxGetRenewUrl(item, cb) {
  var trackCode = item['Track Code'] || 'default';

  if (item['Message Id'] === "on_renew") {
    cxenseOffers.getUserRenewLink(trackCode, function (error, url) {
      if (!error && url) {
        item.url = url;
      }
      if (typeof cb === 'function') {
        cb();
      }
    });
  } else {
    if (typeof cb === 'function') {
      cb();
    }
  }
}

//EDU Redirect May 2022
function cxHandle1PDRedirect(){

  function cb(partialUrl){
    //redirect valid URLs
    var reg = /^(http|https)?:\/\/(partner\.wsj\.com\/p\/)([^\/]|[^\?])*$/i;
    if (reg.test(partialUrl)) {
      window.location.href = partialUrl;
    } else {
      var url = "https://partner.wsj.com/" + redirectUrlSuffix;
      window.location.href = url;
    }
  }

  var key = 'wsj-facultystaffrefresh-ctaurl';
  cxenseOffers.get1stPartyData(key, function (error, partialUrl) {
    if (typeof cb === 'function') {
      cb(partialUrl);
    } 
  });

</style><script type="text/javascript">window.requestAnimationFrame(function() {
  handleCloseButtonClick();

  function handleCloseButtonClick() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $closeButton = $wrapper.querySelector('.close-btn');
    if (!$closeButton) { return; }


    var campaignData;
    try {
      campaignData = JSON.parse($wrapper.dataset.campaign);
    } catch(e) {
      campaignData = {};
    }

    $closeButton.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      campaignData.hideType = 'closeButton';

      if ($closeButton.className.indexOf('gdpr-close') > -1) {
        cxdj.trackPolicy('wsjcpoct2017');
      } else {
        if (campaignData.suppressId) {
          cxdj.annotateUserProfile(campaignData.suppressId);
        }
        cxdj.reportInteractionEvent('notificationClose', campaignData);
      }
      cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50);
    });
  }
});

function cxHandlePageNotificationOmniChannelCheck(item) {
  var campaignData = cxenseOffers.getCampaignData(item);
  cxdj.reportInteractionEvent('notificationView', campaignData);
}

function cxHandlePageNotificationCtaButtonClick(item) {
  var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper');
  var campaignData = cxenseOffers.getCampaignData(item);
  var currentUrl;

  if (window.location.href) {
    currentUrl = encodeURIComponent(window.location.href.replace(window.location.search, ''));
  }

  cxGetRenewUrl(item, function () {
    //Auto Suppress on Button Click if a Suppress Value is found
    if (campaignData.suppressId) {
      cxdj.annotateUserProfile(campaignData.suppressId);
    }
    var redirectUrl = addCurrentUrlToEduRedirectUrl(currentUrl, item.url);

    if (item.campaign === '195' || item.campaign === '130') {
      addTokentoRedirectUrl(redirectUrl, function (redirectUrl) {
        cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50, function () {
          window.location.href = redirectUrl;
        });
      });
    } else {
      cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50, function () {
        window.location.href = redirectUrl;
      });
    }
  });

  function addTokentoRedirectUrl(url, cb) {
    if (!url || url.length === 0) { return; }

    var key = 'wsj-mansion-global-token';

    cxenseOffers.get1stPartyData(key, function (error, token) {
      url += (url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?') + 'token=' + token;
      if (typeof cb === 'function') {
        cb(url);
      }
    });
  }

  function addCurrentUrlToEduRedirectUrl(currentUrl, url) {
    var reg = /^(http|https)?:\/\/(partner\.wsj\.com\/partner\/)([^\/]|[^\?])*$/i;
    var insertPosition;

    if (reg.test(url)) {
      insertPosition = url.indexOf('?');

      if (insertPosition > 0) {
        url = url.substring(0, insertPosition) + (url[insertPosition - 1] === '/' ? '' : '/') + currentUrl + url.substring(insertPosition);
      } else {
        url += (url[url.length - 1] === '/' ? '' : '/') + currentUrl;
      }
    }
    return url;
  }
}

function hok3RaV1() {
  document.querySelector('body').classList.add('hok-3R-V1');

  window.requestAnimationFrame(function () {
    //change description copy
    var copy = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper .notification-description');
    copy.innerText = 'The credit card we have on file for your WSJ membership may be invalid. To avoid any unintended interruptions to your service, please take a moment to update your credit card details now.';

    //change CTA copy
    var cta = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper .notification-action a');
    cta.innerText = 'UPDATE MY CREDIT CARD';

    //change CTA url
    cta.href = 'https://customercenter.wsj.com/payment';

    //pushing the navigation bar down if the banner is visible
    var topDiv = document.querySelector('.style__hat_1vqyrZZ3j7vMCXYKbvaqKa');
    var bannerVisibleOrNot = setInterval(function () {
      if (document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper').style.display !== 'none') {
        clearInterval(bannerVisibleOrNot);
        topDiv.style.marginBottom = '57px';
      } else if (document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper').style.display === 'none') {
        clearInterval(bannerVisibleOrNot);
        topDiv.style.marginBottom = '0px';
      }
    }, 50);

  });

}

function cxHandlePageNotificationAdobeIdCtaButtonClick(item) {
  var redirectUrl = addAdobeIdToRedirectUrl(item.url);
  window.location.href = redirectUrl;

  function addAdobeIdToRedirectUrl(url) {
    if (!url || url.length === 0) { return; }

    var adobeCookie = cxdj.getOmnitureCookieValue();
    if (adobeCookie && adobeCookie.mcmid) {
      url += (url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?') + 'adobeid=' + adobeCookie.mcmid;
    }
    return url;
  }
}

  var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-notification-wrapper');
  var campaignData = cxenseOffers.getCampaignData(item);

  cxGetRenewUrl(item, function () {
    //Auto Suppress on Button Click if a Suppress Value is found

    }

    cxenseOffers.fadeOut($wrapper, 50, function () {
      window.location.href = redirectUrl;
    });
  });

  function addVxidToRedirectUrl(url) {
    if (!url || url.length === 0) { return; }

    var vxid = cxenseOffers.getVxid();
    url += (url.indexOf('?') !== -1 ? '&' : '?') + 'vxid=' + vxid;

function cxGetRenewUrl(item, cb) {
  var trackCode = item['Track Code'] || 'default';

  if (item['Message Id'] === "on_renew") {
    cxenseOffers.getUserRenewLink(trackCode, function (error, url) {
      if (!error && url) {
        item.url = url;
      }
      if (typeof cb === 'function') {
        cb();
      }
    });
  } else {
    if (typeof cb === 'function') {
      cb();
    }
  }
}

/* End Strip Down*/</style><script type="text/javascript">window.requestAnimationFrame(function () {
  handlePopupMouseOver();
  handlePopupMouseLeave();
  handlePopupClick();

  function handlePopupMouseOver() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-popup-wrapper');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $popover = $wrapper.querySelector('.popover');
    if (!$popover) { return; }

    $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseover', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      // Show Popover
      $popover.classList.remove('hide');
      $popover.classList.add('show');
      $popover.classList.remove('fade-out');
      $popover.classList.add('fade-in');
    });
  }

  function handlePopupMouseLeave() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-popup-wrapper');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $popover = $wrapper.querySelector('.popover');
    if (!$popover) { return; }

    $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseleave', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      // Hide Popover
      $popover.classList.remove('fade-in');
      $popover.classList.add('fade-out');

      setTimeout(function () {
        $popover.classList.remove('show');
        $popover.classList.add('hide');
      }, 500);
    });
  }

  function handlePopupClick() {
    var $module = document.querySelector('#cx-popup');
    if (!$module) {
      return;
    }

    $module.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
    });
  }
});

// Subscribe Text Link overwrite for Nonsubs on HP & Section Fronts
const cxHandleCusomterNavSubscribeBtnUpdate = (item) => {
  if (window.innerWidth <= 1300) { return; }
  const {
    url,
    'customer nav subscribe button':  cusNavSubBtnText
  } = item;

  const cusNavSubBtnId = '#cx-customer-nav-subscribe-btn';
  const cusNavSubBtns = document.querySelectorAll(cusNavSubBtnId);

  if (cusNavSubBtns.length == 0) { return; }

  window.requestAnimationFrame( () => {
    cusNavSubBtns.forEach((cusNavSubBtn) => {
      if (url) {
        cusNavSubBtn.href = url + (url.indexOf('?') >= 0 ? '&' : '?') + 'navSource=subscribeTextLink';
      }
      if (cusNavSubBtnText) {
        cusNavSubBtn.innerHTML = cusNavSubBtnText;
      }
    });
  });
};

function cxHandleNonSubTopRhsHeaderClick(item) {
  var suppressId = item['Suppress Value'];
  if (suppressId) {
    cxdj.annotateUserProfile(suppressId);
  }
  window.location.href = item.url;
}


// App Download Experience
// =======================
window.requestAnimationFrame(function(){
  cXhandleDropdownClick();
  handlePopoutMouseOver();
  handlePopoutMouseLeave();

  function cXhandleDropdownClick() {
    var $dropdown = document.querySelector('#cx-popout-wrapper .flag-dropdown');
    var $countryList = document.querySelector('#cx-popout-wrapper .country-list');
    var cXisClicked = false;
    if (!$dropdown) { return; }

    $dropdown.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      if (!cXisClicked) {
        $countryList.classList.remove('hide');
        cXisClicked = true;
      } else {
        $countryList.classList.add('hide');
        cXisClicked = false;
      }
    }, false);
  }

  function handlePopoutMouseOver() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-app-download');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $popover = $wrapper.querySelector('.cx-app-popup');
    if (!$popover) { return; }

    $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseover', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      // Show Popover
      $popover.classList.remove('hide');
      $popover.classList.add('show');
      $popover.classList.remove('fade-out');
      $popover.classList.add('fade-in');
    });
  }

  function handlePopoutMouseLeave() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-app-download');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $popover = $wrapper.querySelector('.cx-app-popup');
    if (!$popover) { return; }

    $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseleave', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();

      // Hide Popover
      $popover.classList.remove('fade-in');
      $popover.classList.add('fade-out');

      setTimeout(function () {
        $popover.classList.remove('show');
        $popover.classList.add('hide');
      }, 500);
    });
  }
});

  sendLink_linkTexting('19d796ae-145d-4a31-8f54-e4abeb032ef4', '');

  function handlePopupMouseOver() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-popup-wrapper');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $popover = $wrapper.querySelector('.popover');
    if (!$popover) { return; }

    $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseover', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      // Show Popover
      $popover.classList.remove('hide');
      $popover.classList.add('show');
      $popover.classList.remove('fade-out');
      $popover.classList.add('fade-in');
    });
  }

  function handlePopupMouseLeave() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-popup-wrapper');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $popover = $wrapper.querySelector('.popover');
    if (!$popover) { return; }

    $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseleave', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      // Hide Popover
      $popover.classList.remove('fade-in');
      $popover.classList.add('fade-out');

      setTimeout(function () {
        $popover.classList.remove('show');
        $popover.classList.add('hide');
      }, 500);
    });

    if (!$module) {
      return;

      event.stopPropagation();
    });
  }

// Subscribe Text Link overwrite for Nonsubs on HP & Section Fronts
const cxHandleCusomterNavSubscribeBtnUpdate = (item) => {
  if (window.innerWidth <= 1300) { return; }
  const {
    url,
    'customer nav subscribe button':  cusNavSubBtnText
  } = item;

  const cusNavSubBtnId = '#cx-customer-nav-subscribe-btn';
  const cusNavSubBtns = document.querySelectorAll(cusNavSubBtnId);

  if (cusNavSubBtns.length == 0) { return; }

  window.requestAnimationFrame( () => {
    cusNavSubBtns.forEach((cusNavSubBtn) => {
      if (url) {
        cusNavSubBtn.href = url + (url.indexOf('?') >= 0 ? '&' : '?') + 'navSource=subscribeTextLink';
      }
      if (cusNavSubBtnText) {
        cusNavSubBtn.innerHTML = cusNavSubBtnText;
      }
    });
  });
};

function cxHandleNonSubTopRhsHeaderClick(item) {
  var suppressId = item['Suppress Value'];
  if (suppressId) {
    cxdj.annotateUserProfile(suppressId);
  }
  window.location.href = item.url;
}


// App Download Experience
// =======================
window.requestAnimationFrame(function(){
  cXhandleDropdownClick();
  handlePopoutMouseOver();
  handlePopoutMouseLeave();

  function cXhandleDropdownClick() {
    var $dropdown = document.querySelector('#cx-popout-wrapper .flag-dropdown');
    var $countryList = document.querySelector('#cx-popout-wrapper .country-list');
    var cXisClicked = false;
    if (!$dropdown) { return; }

    $dropdown.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      if (!cXisClicked) {
        $countryList.classList.remove('hide');
        cXisClicked = true;
      } else {
        $countryList.classList.add('hide');
        cXisClicked = false;
      }
    }, false);
  }

  function handlePopoutMouseOver() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-app-download');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $popover = $wrapper.querySelector('.cx-app-popup');
    if (!$popover) { return; }

    $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseover', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();
      // Show Popover
      $popover.classList.remove('hide');
      $popover.classList.add('show');
      $popover.classList.remove('fade-out');
      $popover.classList.add('fade-in');
    });
  }

  function handlePopoutMouseLeave() {
    var $wrapper = document.querySelector('#cx-app-download');
    if (!$wrapper) { return; }

    var $popover = $wrapper.querySelector('.cx-app-popup');
    if (!$popover) { return; }

    $wrapper.addEventListener('mouseleave', function (event) {
      event.stopPropagation();

      // Hide Popover
      $popover.classList.remove('fade-in');
      $popover.classList.add('fade-out');

      setTimeout(function () {
        $popover.classList.remove('show');
        $popover.classList.add('hide');
      }, 500);
    });
  }
});

  sendLink_linkTexting('19d796ae-145d-4a31-8f54-e4abeb032ef4', '');

  .button-wrapper {
    height: 32px;
    display: flex;
    grid-column: main;
  }

  button {
    /* resets --start-- */
    border: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    width: auto;
    overflow: visible;
    background: transparent;
    color: inherit;
    font: inherit;
    line-height: normal;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: inherit;
    /* resets --end-- */

    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  button .typography {
    font-family: var(--typography-presets-editorial-label010-font-family);
    font-size: var(--typography-presets-editorial-label010-font-size);
    font-stretch: var(--typography-presets-editorial-label010-font-stretch);
    font-weight: var(--typography-presets-editorial-label010-font-weight);
    letter-spacing: var(--typography-presets-editorial-label010-letter-spacing);
    line-height: var(--typography-presets-editorial-label010-line-height);
    text-transform: var(--typography-presets-editorial-label010-text-transform);
  }

  button .svg-wrapper {
    height: 16px;
    width: 16px;
    margin-inline-start: var(--space-presets-space010);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transform: rotateX(var(--icon-rotation));
  }

  button svg {
    color: var(--text-color);
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
  }

  .items-wrapper {
    grid-column: main;
    display: grid;
    visibility: var(--items-visibility);
    grid-template-rows: var(--items-row-height);
    transition: grid-template-rows 200ms ease-in-out;
  }

  .items-wrapper ul {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  ul {
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-presets-space030);
    line-height: 20px;
  }

  /* gap will create space at beginning and end as well */
  ul:before,
  ul:after {
    content: '';
  }

  li {
    margin: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
  }

  li :any-link {
    color: var(--text-color);
    text-decoration-line: underline;

    text-decoration-color: currentColor;

    border-width: 0;
    border-block-start-width: 1px;
    border-style: solid;

    margin: 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

      --items-visibility: visible;

<div id="google_ads_iframe_/2/interactive.wsj.com/market_data_center_4__container__" style="border: 0pt none;"><iframe aria-label="Advertisement" data-google-container-id="4" data-load-complete="true" frameborder="0" height="60" id="google_ads_iframe_/2/interactive.wsj.com/market_data_center_4" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" name="google_ads_iframe_/2/interactive.wsj.com/market_data_center_4" scrolling="no" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom;" tabindex="0" title="3rd party ad content" width="120"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="style--grid--SxS2So51"><div class="style--column--1p190TxH style--column-top--3Nm75EtS style--column-12--1x6zST_y"><div class="WSJBase--u-positionRelative--2XfBrIvu WSJTheme--legalnote__wrapper--PcubUJqP"><div class="WSJTheme--legalnote--2toL5Hj8"><div class="WSJTheme--legalnote__header--32OTT-5K"><button class="WSJForms--btn-link--1JzoW8JZ WSJForms--form-small--3g6ankKK WSJTheme--btn-link--PHWrlJSi">Notes &amp; Data Providers</button></div><div class="WSJTheme--legalnote__text--3ElNnk1x"><div>
<p>Stocks: Real-time U.S. stock quotes reflect trades reported through Nasdaq only; comprehensive quotes and volume reflect trading in all markets and are delayed at least 15 minutes. International stock quotes are delayed as per exchange requirements. Fundamental company data and analyst estimates provided by FactSet. Copyright 2019© FactSet Research Systems Inc. All rights reserved. Source: FactSet</p>
<p>Indexes: Index quotes may be real-time or delayed as per exchange requirements; refer to time stamps for information on any delays. Source: FactSet</p>
<p>Markets Diary: Data on U.S. Overview page represent trading in all U.S. markets and updates until 8 p.m. See <a href="http://online.wsj.com/mdc/public/page/2_3021-tradingdiary2.html">Closing Diaries</a> table for 4 p.m. closing data. Sources: FactSet, Dow Jones</p>
<p>Stock Movers: Gainers, decliners and most actives market activity tables are a combination of NYSE, Nasdaq, NYSE American and NYSE Arca listings. Sources: FactSet, Dow Jones</p>
<p>ETF Movers: Includes ETFs &amp; ETNs with volume of at least 50,000. Sources: FactSet, Dow Jones</p>
<p>Bonds: Bond quotes are updated in real-time. Sources: FactSet, Tullett Prebon</p>
<p>Currencies: Currency quotes are updated in real-time. Sources: FactSet, Tullett Prebon</p>
<p>Commodities &amp; Futures: Futures prices are delayed at least 10 minutes as per exchange requirements. Change value during the period between open outcry settle and the commencement of the next day's trading is calculated as the difference between the last trade and the prior day's settle. Change value during other periods is calculated as the difference between the last trade and the most recent settle. Source: FactSet</p>
<img class="factset_logo" src="https://s.wsj.net/img/factset_logo.png"/>
<p>Data are provided 'as is' for informational purposes only and are not intended for trading purposes. FactSet (a) does not make any express or implied warranties of any kind regarding the data, including, without limitation, any warranty of merchantability or fitness for a particular purpose or use; and (b) shall not be liable for any errors, incompleteness, interruption or delay, action taken in reliance on any data, or for any damages resulting therefrom. Data may be intentionally delayed pursuant to supplier requirements.</p>
<p>Mutual Funds &amp; ETFs: All of the mutual fund and ETF information contained in this display, with the exception of the current price and price history, was supplied by Lipper, A Refinitiv Company, subject to the following: Copyright 2019© Refinitiv. All rights reserved. Any copying, republication or redistribution of Lipper content, including by caching, framing or similar means, is expressly prohibited without the prior written consent of Lipper. Lipper shall not be liable for any errors or delays in the content, or for any actions taken in reliance thereon.</p>
<p>Cryptocurrencies: Cryptocurrency quotes are updated in real-time. Sources: CoinDesk (Bitcoin), Kraken (all other cryptocurrencies)</p>
<p>Calendars and Economy: 'Actual' numbers are added to the table after economic reports are released. Source: Kantar Media</p>

          const relList = link.relList;

            return false;

<script type="text/javascript">
    function isFullScreenMode() {
      if ((document && document.webkitFullscreenElement && document.webkitFullscreenElement.classList.contains('video-wrapper'))
      || (document && document.fullscreenElement && document.fullscreenElement.classList.contains('video-wrapper'))
      || (document && document.msFullscreenElement && document.msFullscreenElement.classList.contains('video-wrapper'))) {
        return true;
      }
      return false;
    }
    window.isFullScreenMode = isFullScreenMode;
  </script>
<script>
if (window.PerformanceObserver) {
  
window._perfMarkAllowedList = [
  'cx-candybar-onload',
  'first-contentful-paint',
  'cx-candybar-onload',
  'gcRendererStart',
  'optimizely:blockBegin',
  'playerLoadStart',
  'playerReady',
  'playerDisplayed',
  'reactAppRenderStart',
  'reactAppRenderEnd'
];

  var observer = new PerformanceObserver(function (list) {
    var entries = list.getEntries();
    var _loop = function _loop(i) {
      var entry = entries[i];
      var metricName = entry.name;
      if ( window._perfMarkAllowedList.indexOf(entry.name) !== -1 ) {
        var time = Math.round(entry.startTime + entry.duration);
        if (metricName === 'gpt-slotOnload' ) {
          if (typeof newrelic !== 'undefined') {
             newrelic.setCustomAttribute(metricName, time);
          }
          setTimeout(function(){observer.disconnect()}, 8000)

        } else {
          if (typeof newrelic !== 'undefined') {
            newrelic.setCustomAttribute(metricName, time);
          }
        }
      }
    };

    for (var i = 0; i < entries.length; i++) {
      _loop(i);
    }

  });
  try {
    observer.observe({
      type: ['mark'], buffered: true
    });
  }
  catch(e) {
    console.log('observer not supported')
  }
}
</script>
